Koga Shuko/Unitron/Sixshot/Unitron/Hades/Anubis/Serpentor:



Koga Shuko laughed at Marine.  Transforming to jet fighter mode, he powered 
up his engines to full, blasting off forward into the air at mach 2 (JP's 
choice on what happens to Marine) <All forces under my command, this is Koga 
Shuko.  Fall back to base.  We will regroup there!>

---

Unitron went into reverse, firing four laser bolts off at autoguns as he went 
into reverse.

---

Hades, Anubis, Serpentor, and Sixshot slowly retreated, all those Newcomers 
heading back towards base to repair.
